{"tid":1708364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員進入港大校園 5名學生被捕 張翔：已表達關注","createTime":"2019-11-11T14:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:48:30.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e713bf74a3f17182666742b94061e3feed63b523","tid":1708364,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"港大校長張翔向師生發信，回應有警員進入校園的事件，指有5名學生被捕，已經去信警務處處長表達關注，並要求警方保障被捕學生的權利。<br />\n<br />\n張翔表示，凌晨1時許，一名學生在薄扶林道被捕、早上7時許有4名學生在警方追截示威者進入校園時被捕。校方表示，接到警方通知，由於有人報案，所以進入校園，校方亦留意到警方在校園內施放催淚彈及胡椒噴劑。<br />\n<br />\n張翔重申，警方有既定程序和指引，除非接獲報案、取得搜查令之外，不得進入校園範圍，但又特別提到，根據規例，警員若懷疑有疑犯身處特定處所，便可以進入相關處所。<br />\n<br />\n張翔表示，明白近日的氣氛緊張，亦對有示威者傷亡感到遺憾，呼籲所有大學成員保持冷靜、理性、以人身安全為首位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491437-20191111.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491437-20191111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=c9eddd4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491437-20191111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b9162c5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491437-20191111.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54655779e458b5026cb0d113bcaa1eddf743fe2e","tid":1708364,"uid":96648,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"達狗啲Fd?"},{"pid":"fff8017f81b27633413539042ca01e0c0cf04ac8","tid":1708364,"uid":324877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e713bf74a3f17182666742b94061e3feed63b523","tid":1708364,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"港大校長張翔向師生發信，回應有警員進入校園的事件，指有5名學生被捕，已經去信警務處處長表達關注，並要求警方保障被捕學生的權利。<br />\n<br />\n張翔表示，凌晨1時許，一名學生在薄扶林道被捕、早上7時許有4名學生在警方追截示威者進入校園時被捕。校方表示，接到警方通知，由於有人報案，所以進入校園，校方亦留意到警方在校園內施放催淚彈及胡椒噴劑。<br />\n<br />\n張翔重申，警方有既定程序和指引，除非接獲報案、取得搜查令之外，不得進入校園範圍，但又特別提到，根據規例，警員若懷疑有疑犯身處特定處所，便可以進入相關處所。<br />\n<br />\n張翔表示，明白近日的氣氛緊張，亦對有示威者傷亡感到遺憾，呼籲所有大學成員保持冷靜、理性、以人身安全為首位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491437-20191111.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491437-20191111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=c9eddd4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491437-20191111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b9162c5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491437-20191111.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"Sorry借一借位<br />\n<br />\n經過今日！天水圍弱點已經發現！入嚟推！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2efa4a3082f24d267bb13822fa8e71e4e1e18b70","tid":1708364,"uid":127177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"在象牙塔一直關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8e4691edfff23866f55e463f63e13620b63181","tid":1708364,"uid":178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"學術界達哥"},{"pid":"213f17d57555d7b36f8a5643a0cde2f57037ef72","tid":1708364,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"beb91403e3846066dfe4d4dd66ee9bb212f53246","tid":1708364,"uid":108606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母關注 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話你唔係共匪都無人信，自己學生比人又拉又鎖你表達關注 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我關注哂你全家女性個閪添呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/n